title: MongoDb, No SQL, ASP.Net, Restful API
description: This is a Restful API Built in C# using ASP.Net, Built for a hypothetical educational institute that collects and queries weather data from sunshine coast weather sensors. It uses MongoDb as a NoSQL database. A C# ASP.Net restful API that uses Repository architecture.

title: Database Integration
description: In this Project we were given an existing website that used CSV files for data storage and we were tasked with implementing an SQL Database solution and a basic login system it was not a requirement that the security was overly secure because we are using this project in a future unit where we will implement a security solution.
